This directory contains several kumac files for crk module.

crk_tst_12stp.kumac
	kumac file to test "12 step" part of CRK module.
	transform data from ghit-->Raw-->FEE-->DCM-->Raw again and
	compare the two Raw data.


dc_crk_run_init.kumac
	initialization for dc_crk_run (run DC reconstruction and RICH)
	This uses the following macros
	   dc_init.kumac
	   dc_par.kumac
	   crk_init.kumac
  dc_init.kumac   initialize DC
  dc_par.kumac    initialize parameters for DC
  crk_init.kumac  initialize Crk
  
dc_crk_run.kumac
	event processing for DC+RICH reconstruction
	usage:  exec dc_crk_run nevent evttype
	        where
			nevent: # of events to process
			evttype: event type. should be hj or sig or mix
	        		hj--> HIJING event (defined in dc_crk_run_init)
				sig--> signal (e.g. 1 electron track event)
				mix--> mix hj and sig

	This uses the following macros
	   dc_1event.kumac
	   crk_1event.kumac
	   crk_clear_event.kumac
	   crk_hbend.kumac
  dc_1event.kumac
	process 1 event (for DC)
  crk_1event.kumac
	process 1 event (for RICH)
  dc_crk_clear_event.kumac
 	clear current event
  crk_hbend.kumac
	HBOOK I/O

